snippet.title: Olaf the Boozer - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The world feels like a complete disaster after a hangover. The furniture is wrecked, and who knows what dwarf Olaf did last night? Help Olaf go through this puzzle, recollect the memories, and dodge angry patrons. Unravel the mystery - is it just a hangover or something more?

Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3001110/Olaf_the_Boozer/
